from(ConstantsRest.ROUTE_ID_UPDATE): This is likely linked to a REST endpoint (e.g., /update).
setExchangePattern(ExchangePattern.InOnly): This is critical. It tells Camel this is an Asynchronous fire-and-forget call. The API will acknowledge the request quickly without waiting for the full background processing to finish.
